# TYPO3 13 upgrade

- Upgrade this extension to TYPO3 13.4 LTS only. Do not keep dual v11/v13 logic unless unavoidable.
- Update version constraints, PHP requirements, and local dev assumptions for TYPO3 13.
- Replace removed APIs and legacy patterns such as `TYPO3_MODE`, TSFE-heavy access, outdated Fluid internals, and deprecated page-tree helpers.
- Prefer TYPO3 13-compatible Extbase controller responses, QueryBuilder/DBAL APIs, and current FlexForm structure.
- Use automation when helpful, but review and refine generated changes manually.

## Report loop

- Write findings to `Build/Reports/typo3-extension-upgrade-report.md`.
- Commit the report before code changes.
- After fixes, validate touched code paths and keep the target strictly TYPO3 13.
